  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are currently positioned just below the massive 7000 gamma wall (+13.9B) after breaking through the 6975 level, creating immediate selling pressure as they hedge short gamma exposure from the wall break. The PIN regime with 100.9B total GEX suggests dealers will aggressively sell any push back toward 7000 while providing support on dips toward the 6895 flip level. Watch for dealers to defend the 6975-7000 zone heavily, with the next significant support at 6895 where the regime would shift if breached.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect strong resistance at 7000 with dealers capping upside moves while supporting any deeper dips.",
